# How Redpanda Seamlessly Generates Pipeline with Bluebirds
[Redpanda](https://redpanda.com) is a startup building in the data streaming space. With a team of 4 ADRs and 12 AEs, they struggled to efficiently target the right accounts and personalize their outreach at scale. Roman Kopytko, Director of Growth at Redpanda, shares how Bluebirds transformed their sales process, leading to remarkable improvements in efficiency and output.
